imdb.plot outline: Cheetay follows the often ill fated but always funny misadventures of three friends (Adeel, Jaleel and Shakeel). Shakeel is a wheeler dealer always looking to make a fast buck. His failed ventures always taking a toll on his faithful wife, Hunya and their son. Jaleel is sub-human and is probably the missing link. His antics are a constant source of misery for his fiery, hot tempered wife Sana. Adeel is a disgraced TV chef with an eye for the ladies. His philandering ways often land him into trouble. The object of his affection is Dr. Saba, Much to her disdain.
